title: Sophisticated Haven In A Premium Lifestyle Enclave - 3138 Market St B
posting_body: ['Capture The Charm, Love The Space, Live The Location', 'Designed with your comfort in mind, the well-designed floor plan features a warm and welcoming interior and incorporates relaxed living spaces.', 'Enjoy the sleek finishes in this thoughtfully designed kitchen that has been well-maintained and boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant countertops.', 'The spacious master bedroom is a secluded retreat that affords a walk-in closet.', 'Sleekly designed, the master bathroom is beautifully appointed with a shower, soaking tub, and sink.', 'In-unit laundry is also available.', 'Set on a quiet street in an incomparable part of Hoover - Foster.', 'Discover all the perks of this active community.', 'Access to shopping is easy thanks to freeways and public transportation just less than a mile away.', "This unique home won't last long.", 'Schedule your private tour today.', '** Tenant pays for electricity, gas, and cable/internet.', '** Security Deposit is equal to 1x the monthly rent based upon approved credit.', '(NOTE: In CA, can increase security deposits to 2x rent.', 'Please see the statement of rental criteria here: <URL>', '**', 'If you are interested in applying, please email', 'show contact info', 'or text', 'show contact info', 'to request an application.', 'Please note that applications are reviewed in the order received and application fees are not refundable.', '**']
